This is a page to gather "wishes" about postgis database configurations.
See ticket #1393.

Example configurations:

 * postgis.out.wkt.precision
 * postgis.out.wkt.standard <string>
 * postgis.out.gml.prefix <string>
 * postgis.debug.level <integer>
  * Note that at debug level 0 the debug code is optimized right out of the compile. I think this one is a nonstarter. (PR)
 * postgis.proj4.search_path <string>:<string>:...
 * postgis.gdal.search_path <string>:<string>:...